  </div>

  <div class="gm:relative gm:mx-auto gm:max-w-[78rem]">
    <div class="gm:mx-auto gm:max-w-[48rem] gm:text-center">
      <h2
        id="gm-res-process-title"
        class="gm:m-0 gm:text-section-heading gm:text-strong gm:[text-wrap:balance]"
      >
        OUR SIMPLE PROCESS
      </h2>
      <p
        class="gm:m-0 gm:mx-auto gm:mt-5 gm:max-w-[46rem] gm:text-section-body gm:text-copy-muted"
      >
        From the first phone call to the final polish, we make glass replacement
        easy.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div
