      >
        <li class="gm:h-full">
          <article
            class="gm:flex gm:min-h-[15.5rem] gm:flex-col gm:rounded-[1.5rem] gm:border gm:border-white/70 gm:bg-[linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(255,255,255,0.96)_0%,rgba(249,252,255,0.92)_100%)] gm:p-6 gm:shadow-card gm:backdrop-blur-sm gm:sm:min-h-[16.5rem] gm:sm:p-7 gm:lg:min-h-[17.5rem]"
          >
            <p class="gm:m-0 gm:text-process-step gm:text-secondary/20">01</p>
            <h3
              class="gm:m-0 gm:mt-4 gm:text-card-heading gm:text-primary gm:[text-wrap:balance]"
            >
              Inspection &amp; Quote
            </h3>
            <p
              class="gm:m-0 gm:mt-4 gm:max-w-[30ch] gm:text-content-body gm:text-copy"
            >
              We visit your home to inspect the damage, measure the glass, and
              provide a clear, written estimate.
            </p>
          </article>
        </li>

        <li class="gm:h-full">
          <article
            class="gm:flex gm:min-h-[15.5rem] gm:flex-col gm:rounded-[1.5rem] gm:border gm:border-white/70 gm:bg-[linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(255,255,255,0.96)_0%,rgba(249,252,255,0.92)_100%)] gm:p-6 gm:shadow-card gm:backdrop-blur-sm gm:sm:min-h-[16.5rem] gm:sm:p-7 gm:lg:min-h-[17.5rem]"
          >
            <p class="gm:m-0 gm:text-process-step gm:text-secondary/20">02</p>
            <h3
              class="gm:m-0 gm:mt-4 gm:text-card-heading gm:text-primary gm:[text-wrap:balance]"
            >
              Glass Fabrication
            </h3>
            <p
              class="gm:m-0 gm:mt-4 gm:max-w-[31ch] gm:text-content-body gm:text-copy"
            >
              We order or fabricate glass to your exact specs&mdash;single-pane,
              tempered safety glass, or energy-efficient double-pane (IGU) units
              with the right Low-E and thickness.
            </p>
          </article>
        </li>

        <li class="gm:h-full">
          <article
            class="gm:flex gm:min-h-[15.5rem] gm:flex-col gm:rounded-[1.5rem] gm:border gm:border-white/70 gm:bg-[linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(255,255,255,0.96)_0%,rgba(249,252,255,0.92)_100%)] gm:p-6 gm:shadow-card gm:backdrop-blur-sm gm:sm:min-h-[16.5rem] gm:sm:p-7 gm:lg:min-h-[17.5rem]"
          >
            <p class="gm:m-0 gm:text-process-step gm:text-secondary/20">03</p>
            <h3
              class="gm:m-0 gm:mt-4 gm:text-card-heading gm:text-primary gm:[text-wrap:balance]"
            >
              Professional Installation
            </h3>
            <p
              class="gm:m-0 gm:mt-4 gm:max-w-[30ch] gm:text-content-body gm:text-copy"
            >
              We carefully remove the old glass, clean the frame, install the
              new unit, and seal it against the weather.
            </p>
          </article>
        </li>

        <li class="gm:h-full">
          <article
            class="gm:flex gm:min-h-[15.5rem] gm:flex-col gm:rounded-[1.5rem] gm:border gm:border-white/70 gm:bg-[linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(255,255,255,0.96)_0%,rgba(249,252,255,0.92)_100%)] gm:p-6 gm:shadow-card gm:backdrop-blur-sm gm:sm:min-h-[16.5rem] gm:sm:p-7 gm:lg:min-h-[17.5rem]"
          >
            <p class="gm:m-0 gm:text-process-step gm:text-secondary/20">04</p>
            <h3
              class="gm:m-0 gm:mt-4 gm:text-card-heading gm:text-primary gm:[text-wrap:balance]"
            >
              Final Walkthrough
            </h3>
            <p
              class="gm:m-0 gm:mt-4 gm:max-w-[30ch] gm:text-content-body gm:text-copy"
            >
              We ensure the window opens and closes correctly and that the glass
              is spotless before we leave.
            </p>
          </article>
        </li>
      </ol>

      <div class="gm:mx-auto gm:w-full gm:max-w-[34rem] gm:lg:max-w-none">
        <div class="gm:relative">
          <div
            class="gm:pointer-events-none gm:absolute gm:-right-5 gm:-top-5 gm:h-28 gm:w-28 gm:rounded-full gm:bg-secondary/18 gm:blur-3xl gm:sm:-right-6 gm:sm:-top-6 gm:sm:h-32 gm:sm:w-32"
